            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社17日專訊》騰訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)一度升逾3%,最高價見461.6元,升穿10天線(452.26元),現升3%,報461.4元,較ADR收市高出2.9%,最低價449.8元;成交1533萬股,成交金額69.99億元;主動買沽比率60:40,資金淨主動買入12.93億元。現時最大淨被動買入券商為美銀,金額2.44億元,加權平均成交價457.142元;現時最大淨被動賣出券商為花旗環球金融亞洲,金額3.98億元,加權平均成交價456.549元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　另外,其<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>櫃台股份(80700-HK)升3.1%,報434元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>,最高價434元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>,最低價424元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>;成交5900股,成交金額253.83萬<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報21406,升349點或1.7%;恒生中國企業指數報7908,升129點或1.7%;恒生科技指數報4907,升111點或2.3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　基本資料</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　====</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>現價</td><td>461.400</td><td>變動</td><td>+2.99%</td></tr><tr><td>最高價</td><td>461.600</td><td>最低價</td><td>449.800</td></tr><tr><td>成交股數</td><td>1533萬股</td><td>成交金額</td><td>69.99億</td></tr><tr><td>10天平均</td><td>452.260</td><td>歷史波幅%</td><td>51.687</td></tr><tr><td>20天平均</td><td>479.930</td><td>加權平均價</td><td>456.445</td></tr><tr><td>50天平均</td><td>487.330</td><td>RSI14</td><td>44.095</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　股份狀態:升穿10天線;主動買沽比率60:40,資金淨主動買入12.93億元</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>騰訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00700:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00700\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00700-HK</a>)</td><td>461.40</td><td>+2.99</td></tr><tr><td>快手(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01024:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01024\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01024-HK</a>)</td><td>50.35</td><td>+3.39</td></tr><tr><td>小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)</td><td>42.05</td><td>+1.94</td></tr><tr><td>貝殼-W(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02423:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02423\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02423-HK</a>)</td><td>53.20</td><td>+6.61</td></tr><tr><td>美團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03690:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03690\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03690-HK</a>)</td><td>136.10</td><td>+0.89</td></tr><tr><td>京東集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09618:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09618-HK</a>)</td><td>139.40</td><td>+0.72</td></tr><tr><td>小鵬汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09868:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09868\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09868-HK</a>)</td><td>75.10</td><td>+2.39</td></tr><tr><td>攜程(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09961:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09961\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09961-HK</a>)</td><td>444.00</td><td>+1.74</td></tr><tr><td>阿里(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)</td><td>108.60</td><td>+3.04</td></tr><tr><td>騰訊控股-R(80700-HK)</td><td>434.00人幣</td><td>+3.09</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
